At this point it occurs to me that Valis may operate on a Taoistic binary dialectic system, wherein the "dark counter player" is in a sense Mind split into antithetical Forms I and II for the purpose of generating change;

"One Mind there is, but under it two principles contend."

It is a priori knowledge (i.e. omniscience) versus physical power (i.e. omnipotence). White knows everything; Black can do everything (possible). Strange...but that's what seem to characterize the two sides of the dial
